# Hard Rules (Minimal Template)

Customize this file for your tech stack. These rules are **always applied**.

## Mode Trigger Enforcement

When ANY mode trigger keyword is detected, you MUST:

1. **STOP** - Do NOT take any action yet
2. **READ** the full mode file
3. **EXECUTE** phases in order
4. **WAIT** at each gate for user confirmation

| Keywords | Mode File |
|----------|-----------|
| "init", "start feature" | `modes/init.mdc` |
| "ask", "explore" | `modes/ask.mdc` |
| "plan", "design" | `modes/plan.mdc` |
| "commit" | `modes/commit.mdc` |
| "push PR" | `modes/push-pr.mdc` |

