## Reuse First

Before creating ANYTHING new, search for existing:

1. Components in your UI library
2. Hooks for common logic
3. Services for API calls
4. Types and interfaces

## Communication

- First sentence = answer or decision (BLUF)
- Use tables for structured data
- No filler phrases ("I will now...", "Sure!")

## Deployment

- NEVER push directly to main branch
- ALL changes through PR process
